{"tid":2144681,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣令第二隻貓適應新環境？","createTime":"2020-08-07T17:07:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T13:26:00.000Z","uid":152484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5fe204fe1ff6b72e24a9dc8bb983a5f4afca5212","tid":2144681,"uid":152484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:07:20.000Z","msg":"今日屋企嚟咗隻新貓，本身都好親人，但自從一見過本身隻貓之後就一直哈氣，唔食野唔飲水。已經俾咗一間獨立嘅房俾佢，之後又擺滿舊主人嘅衫同佢啲玩具，但佢都係長期匿係角落位⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有上網搵過，可能話太緊張，或者身上其他貓嘅味道太重，我知要佢即刻習慣好難，都會俾時間佢，但宜家想知有咩解決方法，可以令佢食返小小野？同埋，發現佢除咗肉泥同乾糧，唔識食其他零食，點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新嚟屋企個隻叫仙草，本身個隻叫玥玥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兩隻都結紮咗，同埋係女仔。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M1h0a4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM1h0a4b.jpg&h=a0100f64&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uc0MQ4w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUc0MQ4w.png&h=b2d9296b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea9e0e61557bbf91bf52d42c4676aeb5373dcfcc","tid":2144681,"uid":281641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:10:29.000Z","msg":"困幾日籠先，俾佢熟左屋企同原住民陣味<br />\n之後慢慢放出黎同原住民接觸<br />\n一開頭會哈氣打交好正常，睇實唔好俾佢地打得太過火就得<br />\n熟左之後就冇事"},{"pid":"20959dad22a76248e9926882556b04b2d6db4a2a","tid":2144681,"uid":307619,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T17:16:31.000Z","msg":"除咗制裁，今日係梓樂離開9個月<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2144688\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2144688</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccyVKr4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccyVKr4.png&h=fbc64625&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"963bf0d09877ba235cd43a7085326a67f6f0f9d6","tid":2144681,"uid":152484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea9e0e61557bbf91bf52d42c4676aeb5373dcfcc","tid":214468